The Great Game is a tale of high adventure.

00:01:12.812 --> 00:01:19.952
Of spymanship, and of what we can call ‘derring-do’, of great courage and bravery.

00:01:21.252 --> 00:01:26.472
It is the story of young adventurers, British and Russian, who

00:01:26.672 --> 00:01:31.802
grappled for power and influence in central Asia in the 19th century.

00:01:33.342 --> 00:01:39.342
It’s the sort of thing that sounds almost completely invented, something

